{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-entry-js","path":"/notes/py/special_methods/string","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"String Representation"},"html":"<h3>Describing String Representations</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>The class method <code class=\"language-text\">__format__()</code> has the following properties:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Called by the <code class=\"language-text\">format()</code> function</li>\n<li>In other words, <code class=\"language-text\">format</code> just calls <code class=\"language-text\">obj.__format__</code></li>\n<li>Provides the object with a format method that performs some formatting operation</li>\n<li>Can be thought of as syntactic sugar</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>The class method <code class=\"language-text\">__repr__()</code> has the following properties:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Its goal is to be unambiguous</li>\n<li>Should be implemented for any class to provide the class with a useful identity</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>The class method <code class=\"language-text\">__str__()</code> has the following properties:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Its goal is to be readable</li>\n<li>Can be implemented if there is a more readable string representation</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>The following class uses these special methods:</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Document</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> \n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>     <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">__init__</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> words<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> \n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>         self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>words <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> words\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>     <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">__repr__</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>         t <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>         <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>words<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>            t <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> t <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\\n'</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>         <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> t\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>     <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">__str__</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>         <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Document: '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>words \n\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> d <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Document<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'my doc'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> d\nm\ny\n\nd\no\nc\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token builtin\">repr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>d<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'m\\ny\\n \\nd\\no\\nc\\n'</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token builtin\">str</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>d<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'Document: my doc'</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Summarizing Special Methods</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Method</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">__format__</code></td>\n<td>Creates a formatted representation</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">__repr__</code></td>\n<td>Creates a string representation of an object</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">__str__</code></td>\n<td>Creates a simple string representation</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>References</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://index-of.co.uk/Python/Python%20Essential%20Reference,%20Fourth%20Edition.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Python Essential Reference</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/2626364/12777044\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Use-Cases for Each Special Method</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/16683882/12777044\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Description of the <strong>format</strong> Special Method</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.programiz.com/python-programming/methods/built-in/format\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Example of format Special Method</a></li>\n</ul>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"py/special_methods/string","previousSlug":"py/special_methods/creation","nextSlug":"py/special_methods/comparison","previousTitle":"Creation and Deletion","nextTitle":"Comparison and Ordering"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}